summary: 10 years geomodeling experience in E&P and software industry (Schlumberger and Baker Hughes). A combination of Geophysics and Geology background, a master degree in Reservoir Geology - TU Delft, The Netherlands, and bachelor degree in Geophysics - ITB Indonesia.
